## Fungsi Rekursif

Barisan Fibonacci: 0, 1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, ...

$$F_0 = 0, \quad F_1 = 1$$

$$F_n = F_{n-1} + F_{n-2}$$

::: {#90c5d166 .cell execution_count=41}
``` {.python .cell-code}
def fib(n):
  if (n == 0):
    return 0
  elif (n == 1):
    return 1
  else:
    return fib(n-1) + fib(n-2)
```
:::


